# Portfolio Content

## Project pages

- MDX lives in `src/app/work/projects/<slug>.mdx`
- Slug must match filename; routing via `src/app/work/[slug]/page.tsx`
- New project: add MDX + entry in `src/resources/content.js` if it appears on home/work index

## content.js

- Central copy for hero, about snippets, featured project list
- Edit here first when copy spans multiple routes
- Do not duplicate long paragraphs across MDX and content.js

## Components

- Colocate SCSS modules (`*.module.scss`) with components
- Prefer extending Once UI primitives over one-off inline styles
- `"use client"` only for hooks, browser APIs, or interactivity

## Public assets

- Resume: `public/resume_ai_engineer.pdf` — update PDF + links together
- Trademarks/icons: `public/trademarks/`
- Regenerate icons via `node scripts/generate-icons.cjs` when branding changes

## Quality check

```bash
pnpm lint
```

Verify project card renders on `/work` and slug page loads after MDX changes.
